      <details class="mb-4 p-4 border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-bold text-on-surface flex justify-between items-center">
          How do I calculate how many panels I need for machinery?
          <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">▼</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Measure your machinery length, width, and height, then add 10–15cm clearance on all sides. Quinocycle can calculate panel requirements based on your equipment dimensions and weight.
        </p>
      </details>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12 p-8 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg">
      <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Protect Your Machinery with Honeycomb Panels</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">
