        <a href="tel:+60168916381" class="bg-surface-variant/50 border border-primary/20 text-on-surface font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-variant transition text-center">
          Call +6016-8916381
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary mt-4">📧 Email: quinocycle@gmail.com | 📍 Balakong, Selangor</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed">
        For machinery and industrial equipment shipping in Malaysia, honeycomb cardboard panels represent the optimal balance of protection, weight, and cost. With 16+ years supplying industrial companies across Peninsular Malaysia, Quinocycle understands the specific packaging needs of machinery exporters and manufacturers. Custom design, expert sizing, and fast delivery make us the trusted choice for protecting high-value equipment.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mt-4">
